	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">John Smedley Hints at SOE's Next MMORPG Title in CNN Interview</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Tom "Aidden" Hassell</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Apr 27, 2005, 14:58</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=John%20Smedley%20Hints%20at%20SOE%27s%20Next%20MMORPG%20Title%20in%20CNN%20Interview&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Fnews%2FSOE%2Fnews_81.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
